sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Utente (Browser)
    participant CORS as CORS Middleware
    participant EX as ExceptionHandlingMiddleware
    participant RL as RateLimiter
    participant AuthMw as Authentication/Authorization
    participant EP as Endpoint (es. POST /api/customers)
    participant MED as MediatR Pipeline
    participant LOG as LoggingBehavior
    participant VAL as ValidationBehavior
    participant H as Handler (es. CreateCustomerHandler)
    participant REPO as ICustomerRepository
    participant DB as MongoDB
    participant AUDIT as AuditLogRepository

    U->>CORS: HTTP request + Bearer JWT
    CORS->>EX: next()
    EX->>RL: next() (try/catch attorno a tutta la pipeline)
    RL->>AuthMw: next() (se sotto soglia policy)
    AuthMw->>EP: next() (JWT valido + RequireClaim permessi soddisfatto)
    EP->>MED: mediator.Send(command)
    MED->>LOG: invoke()
    LOG->>VAL: invoke() (logga inizio/fine + durata)
    VAL->>VAL: esegue IValidator<TRequest>
    alt validazione fallita
        VAL-->>EX: throw ValidationException
        EX-->>U: 400 ProblemDetails (errors per campo)
    else validazione ok
        VAL->>H: invoke()
        H->>REPO: InsertAsync(doc)
        REPO->>DB: insert
        H->>AUDIT: InsertAsync(AuditLogDocument)
        AUDIT->>DB: insert
        H-->>EP: Response
        EP-->>U: 200/201 OK
    end
